        {
            "title": "周大福上兩月中港同店銷售回復增長1.3% 內地微跌2.7%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">周大福(01929)公布業績的同時，亦披露今年4至5月份營運數字，情況有所改善，中港同店銷售增長更回復正數。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：周大福官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1000x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240604_FI_source-web_01929-8.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：周大福官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1000x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240604_FI_source-web_01929-8.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：周大福官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">在今年4至5月份，周大福在香港及澳門的同店銷售增長+1.3%；內地同店銷售則仍有負增長，數字是-2.7%。同店銷量方面，中港市場同店銷售增長為-8.4%，內地為-9.1%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內周大福零售值增長-1.7%，其中內地增長-2.9%，香港、澳門及其他市場則同樣回復正增長，數字為+6.3%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15005004-%e5%91%a8%e5%a4%a7%e7%a6%8f%e4%b8%8a%e5%85%a9%e6%9c%88%e4%b8%ad%e6%b8%af%e5%90%8c%e5%ba%97%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e5%9b%9e%e5%be%a9%e5%a2%9e%e9%95%b71-3-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0%e5%be%ae%e8%b7%8c2-7",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250609_FI_source-web_01929.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-12 17:05:30",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "周大福全年溢跌近9%  末期息0.32元全年派息減約5.45%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">周大福(01929)公布，截至2025年3 月 31 日年度內，股東應佔溢利59.16億元，較去年同期64.99億元跌8.97%，每股盈利0.59元，按年減8.9%，末期息0.32元，較去年同期0.3元高6.67%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">全年派息0.52元，較去年0.55元跌5.45%。派息比率87.7%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：周大福官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240912_FI_source-web_01929-Central.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：周大福官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240912_FI_source-web_01929-Central.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：周大福官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">營業額896.56億元，按年跌17.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">經營溢利147.46億元，按年升9.8%，經營溢利率16.4%，高於去年的12.4%，毛利率由去年的24%，升至今年的29.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地零售點6274家，按年減896家，同店銷售降19.4%，香港及澳門銷售點87家，按年無變動，同店銷售跌26.1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">電子商務零售值升3.6%，佔集團零售值5.8%，平均售價2500元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15004940-%e5%91%a8%e5%a4%a7%e7%a6%8f%e5%85%a8%e5%b9%b4%e6%ba%a2%e8%b7%8c%e8%bf%919-%e6%9c%ab%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af0-32%e5%85%83%e5%85%a8%e5%b9%b4%e6%b4%be%e6%81%af%e6%b8%9b%e7%b4%845-45",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/bplib_20230710-172142_source-web_01929.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-12 16:55:29",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "舜宇5月份手機鏡頭出貨量按年降5.2% 車載鏡頭則升28.4%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">舜宇光學(02382)公布，今年5月份手機鏡頭出貨量9809.9萬件，按年跌5.2%；車載鏡頭出貨量則達1070.6件，按年升28.4%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"舜宇光學官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/02382-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"舜宇光學官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/02382-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">舜宇光學官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司解釋，期內車載鏡頭出貨量增加，主要因為客戶端需求提升。至於其他光學零件中，玻璃球面鏡片出貨量212.7萬件，按年減少17.1%；其他鏡頭則達1053.3萬件，按年大升51.3%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">光電產品方面，手機攝像模組出貨量3772.9萬件，按年減少17.1%，主要是因為公司專注於中高端案子，且產品結構較去年同期顯著改善。其他光電產品出貨量484.4萬件，按年升44.8%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">顯微儀器5月份出貨量也有1620.7萬件，較去年同期增加4.1%。</p>\n</div>",
